high_descs: Walk to the right side of the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the top of the toilet.
Walk around the toilet to the sink on the left side of the counter top.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the garbage can in the corner.
Put the bar of soap in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap in a garbage can.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the bathtub, then turn left and walk across the room,then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the pink bar of soap that is behind the roll of toilet paper.
Turn left and take two steps, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Place the soap in the right side of the sink. Turn the faucet on for three seconds, then turn the faucet off and take the soap from the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room.
Place the soap in the silver bucket.
Look around and face the toilet bowl
Pick up the pink paper towel at the tank cover.
Look around and face the sink
Put it at the sink. Run the water and makes it wet. Pick it up again.
Turn right and left to find the trash.
Throw the pink paper towel at the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw the wet pink paper towel at the trash bin.
